":504712,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n係人地眼中<br />\n佢咪又係蝗蟲賤種<br />\n又係炒炒賣賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939ad43f1efc863ed478ae4214cacf5f01c6d223","tid":504712,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n係人地眼中<br />\n佢咪又係蝗蟲賤種<br />\n又係炒炒賣賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來買樓收租就係蝗蟲行徑，長見識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8112e6c5e8def323075326c721b62f0b2cd72b","tid":504712,"uid":28549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n人地有開公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要將d多餘錢咩生意都做或者放落月餅罐先得"},{"pid":"3ddf8fb06b8ccb64afbb7bd6ba2834577f7318fa","tid":504712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n係人地眼中<br />\n佢咪又係蝗蟲賤種<br />\n又係炒炒賣賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來買樓收租就係蝗蟲行徑，長見識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買樓收租=支那垃圾DNA"},{"pid":"33e67ff5e316f712bb88fb5fedae243341263684","tid":504712,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"奧地利係唔係剛剛選出極右做總理"},{"pid":"f2137ab96f48e9de94e247d9b6746be5d9c20efb","tid":504712,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"232e444393f935ad6e667bb3e00766ce3fe24891","tid":504712,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧地利係唔係剛剛選出極右做總理</blockquote><br />\n右唔右都唔關佢事啦，去咗30年，鬼佬朋友多過乜啦"},{"pid":"d7821b1e78f569776ff47b019a9097ef8465f723","tid":504712,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n係人地眼中<br />\n佢咪又係蝗蟲賤種<br />\n又係炒炒賣賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來買樓收租就係蝗蟲行徑，長見識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買樓收租=支那垃圾DNA</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282c72b43de015b929277064c7fb135214033341","tid":504712,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母過到去都係買樓收租炒樓</blockquote><br />\n係人地眼中<br />\n佢咪又係蝗蟲賤種<br />\n又係炒炒賣賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來買樓收租就係蝗蟲行徑，長見識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔係蝗蟲行徑；近年加拿大都有中東難民，有班中東業主就將自已手頭租唔出既物業經 ngo 租比班難民。<br />\n不過佢應該講漏野；正路，外國對非自住既屋租金收入同買、賣，係抽好重稅，一係佢唔報囉，一係唔知"},{"pid":"5eaab87027984706efed047d41779cb4b66aeaf6","tid":504712,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"一隻雞蛋30元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df0e75a811e432b59237df5d9e3a2e2e441af4","tid":504712,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一隻雞蛋30元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aed067f523d655fecb0a43800cc69f5fb4dc4d9","tid":504712,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧地利：每人200呎係基本權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港：納米樓都爭住排隊買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[外出用膳]<br />\n奧地利：book檯 table manner系基本<br />\n香港：間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住TVB系基本"},{"pid":"fa4f7ad577470b37bfcf1eef65cea7bbe5cb5cba","tid":504712,"uid":68571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一隻雞蛋30元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都諗左好耐望左幾次<br />\n雞蛋仲貴過菜<br />\n見到你講，我又拉返上去<br />\n都望左陣先睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30abd028fd760251d183ba9b3b23770cb054bce","tid":504712,"uid":49747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己搬過去都算<br />\n仲要幫啲蛔簽紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你話華人賤種係咪特別賤格</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收難民幾萬蚊填張表，唔通要話俾記者知唱通街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}